#: src/rust-2021/index.md:1
msgid "Rust 2021"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2021/index.md:3
msgid ""
"🚧 The 2021 Edition has not yet been released and hence this section is "
"still \"under construction\". You can [read more about our plans in this "
"blog post](https://blog.rust-lang.org/2021/05/11/edition-2021.html)."
msgstr ""

